data.description: FIVE bedroom home minutes from 1-24/Exit 8, area schools and FTC. This charming home offers so much space with high ceilings, decorative trim work, blinds, stainless appliances, spacious primary suite, large rooms and plenty of storage. The flex space could be an office, work out room or an additional bedroom. The over-sized garage (23x26) has a walk out door and is large enough for a boat or work bench. Outside there is a covered deck and fenced in back yard. If you are looking for a new home with room to grow - this is IT! Schedule an appointment to tour this home today!
